  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1998-04-29", 
    "text": "Internal Revenue Service Random Audit Prohibition Act - Amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to Internal Revenue Service audit authority, to: (1) require an examination notice to identify the purpose and basis for such examination; and (2) prohibit random audits and provide civil damages for their knowing performance."
